{"tid":2095354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區議員掛旗 警闖辦事處恐嚇拘捕","createTime":"2020-07-05T11:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:46:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b98bd85a4cf4194546da0a5223c58fdb289600e","tid":2095354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/WGF4RSBAZVSV5WTP2N4DZAP33U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FWGF4RSBAZVSV5WTP2N4DZAP33U%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj396RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=dc3e2c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FWGF4RSBAZVSV5WTP2N4DZAP33U%2F&h=a0f57dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/WGF4RSBAZVSV5WTP2N4DZAP33U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n區議員掛旗 警闖辦事處恐嚇拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】公民黨沙田區議員黃文萱辦事處昨開張，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n批評警方亂「搬龍門」打壓。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：職員指覆檢大量書籍從未見 或歷時半年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-msUXFEz5T-TAFOUKuO4amjbETw=/640x478/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4EFBTLF2VYYOTKJ2YIU5SJCXPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-msUXFEz5T-TAFOUKuO4amjbETw%3D%2F640x478%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4EFBTLF2VYYOTKJ2YIU5SJCXPU.jpg&h=5f825899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田區議員黃文萱的辦事處掛有一幅反轉的「光時」旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃文萱：理直氣壯就夠<br />\n<br />\n辦事處於昨午3時開張，多名警員一早到場部署，活動甫開始，在場至少五名軍裝及便衣警突一擁而上，有便衣在辦事處門外拍攝，亦有軍裝警闖入辦事處內。當時辦事處掛有一幅反轉的旗幟，印有「光復香港 時代革命」字句，警方指旗幟涉違反國安法，要求拆除。事件擾攘一番後，警員登記黃文萱及在場職員的身份證資料後離開，警告若再掛起有關旗幟，稍後或派員拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ndmF8lPhIqpktOwBL_3EgImdnpE=/387x546/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6AK7TVVFPSI5PL6S2KKHLVNHHM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FndmF8lPhIqpktOwBL_3EgImdnpE%3D%2F387x546%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6AK7TVVFPSI5PL6S2KKHLVNHHM.gif&h=4941aedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數名軍裝警闖入議辦要求拆除旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n黃文萱批評警方<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n她續稱自己在9個月前參選區選時，曾向選舉主任解釋過政綱所指「光時」絕無任何顛覆國家含意，而選舉主任亦接納其解釋，不明白當局為何如今又藉此指她違法，實屬無稽。<br />\n<br />\n被問及會否清理議辦內的敏感物品，黃文萱直言會生活如常，「你要做咩就繼續做，做人理直氣壯就足夠」，她更強調儘管惡法臨下，自己亦不會畏懼退縮。公民黨其後發聲明，批評涉事警員借國安法之名，滋擾黃文萱辦事處，是製造白色恐怖，並譴責警方行為，重申要求當局撤回國安法。"},{"pid":"7725a1aa935d8fd256d82f9957b56fc52012d08f","tid":2095354,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"蘋果貼全文"}]}